    "in_reply_to": "Not in-reply-to; this is a day-zero inbox capture for a vacant seat that is about to be staffed.",
    "originating_user_signal": "Director 2026-05-24: 'I think we are getting ready for an implementer, especially because the web site is now seriously out of date. Do you want to draft up a memo for the implementer?' Direct PO direction to draft the staffing-inbox memo.",
